(241, 1, '2017-09-20 17:36:41', '2017-09-20 17:36:41', '<p style="text-align: left;">Our scope of practice is to enhance the components of fitness for our clients.\r\nWe bolster proper exercise that may result in improved body composition, physical performance, and heart condition and health outcomes and we pay close attention to our client''s exercise form, workout routine, and nutrition plan. We achieve this by measuring the body mass index (BMI), body fat percentage (BFP), and body age to our customer’s. The most important is to educate our customers with nutrition guidelines. This service approach combined with the desire to be a successful company, can offer you an experience that will change your lifestyle completely to a better and healthier you.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">In short, we define personalized training as that safe, effective and efficient physical exercise service that reduces the risk of injury and maximizes positive results.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">En síntesis, definimos el entrenamiento personalizado como aquel servicio de ejercicio físico seguro, eficaz y eficiente que reduce el riesgo de lesión y maximiza los resultados positivos.</p>', 'Private Training', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '19-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-09-20 17:36:41', '2017-09-20 17:36:41', '', 19, 'http://angelicasfitnessnutrition.com/2017/09/20/19-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
