(258, 1, '2017-09-21 00:57:56', '2017-09-21 00:57:56', '<strong>Tip </strong>#1<strong> Eat right</strong>\r\n\r\nincludes dried fruits in your food,\r\nsuch as almonds and walnuts.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Tips </strong>#2<strong> Time</strong>\r\n\r\n"Schedule the exercise as if it were another important appointment. It is recommended to accommodate it within the day at a specific time."\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Tips </strong>#3<strong> combination</strong>.\r\n\r\nWeight training in combination with aerobic exercise sessions have been shown to produce tremendous health benefits.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Tip </strong>#4<strong> People</strong>\r\n\r\nThe environment should be surrounded by people with the same goal, helps to train harder and eliminate the laziness of exercise.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Tip </strong>#5<strong> People.</strong>\r\n\r\nGreen juice in the morning, kale, ginger, pineapple. excellent diuretic and antioxidant. Improves constipation problems and helps to lose weight, optional, green apple.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Tip </strong>#6<strong> Rest.</strong>\r\n\r\nMuscles grow while you rest. Do not think that you can develop a good muscular body if you do not get enough sleep.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', '6 Basic tips', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '83-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-09-21 00:57:56', '2017-09-21 00:57:56', '', 83, 'http://angelicasfitnessnutrition.com/2017/09/21/83-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
