(255, 1, '2017-09-27 17:55:31', '2017-09-27 17:55:31', '&nbsp;\n\n<img class="size-medium wp-image-278" src="http://angelicasfitnessnutrition.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/WIA_TIPSportadaweb-300x87.png" alt="" width="300" height="87" />\n\nThe advice is never over, and from a very young age I always like to help others, that''s why I left you a couple of tips here to improve your health.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<strong>Tip </strong>#1<strong> Eat right</strong>\n\nincludes dried fruits in your food, such as almonds and walnuts.\n\n<img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-272" src="http://angelicasfitnessnutrition.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/WIA_TIPS1-300x300.png" alt="" width="300" height="300" />\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<strong>Tips </strong>#2<strong> Time</strong>\n\n"Schedule the exercise as if it were another important appointment. It is recommended to accommodate it within the day at a specific time."\n\n<img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-273" src="http://angelicasfitnessnutrition.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/WIA_TIP2time-300x300.png" alt="" width="300" height="300" />\n\n<strong>Tips </strong>#3<strong> combination</strong>.\n\nWeight training in combination with aerobic exercise sessions have been shown to produce tremendous health benefits.\n\n<img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-274" src="http://angelicasfitnessnutrition.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/WIA_TIPS-combiantion3-300x300.png" alt="" width="300" height="300" />\n\n<strong>Tip </strong>#4<strong> People</strong>\n\nThe environment should be surrounded by people with the same goal, helps to train harder and eliminate the laziness of exercise.\n\n<img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-275" src="http://angelicasfitnessnutrition.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/WIA_TIPS4_people-300x300.png" alt="" width="300" height="300" />\n\n<strong>Tip </strong>#5<strong> People.</strong>\n\nGreen juice in the morning, kale, ginger, pineapple. excellent diuretic and antioxidant. Improves constipation problems and helps to lose weight, optional, green apple.\n\n<img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-276" src="http://angelicasfitnessnutrition.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/WIA_TIPS5juice-300x300.png" alt="" width="300" height="300" />\n\n<strong>Tip </strong>#6<strong> Rest.</strong>\n\nMuscles grow while you rest. Do not think that you can develop a good muscular body if you do not get enough sleep.\n\n<img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-277" src="http://angelicasfitnessnutrition.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/WIA_TIPS6RESt-300x300.png" alt="" width="300" height="300" />\n\nI hope these tips have served you and you can improve every day more, remember that rest is vital. Sleep well guys.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;', '6 Basic tips', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '83-autosave-v1', '', '', '2017-09-27 17:55:31', '2017-09-27 17:55:31', '', 83, 'http://angelicasfitnessnutrition.com/2017/09/21/83-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
